title: Football participation England 2016 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of participants. In total the number of data points it has is 4.
In general Number of participants has fallen over the Year.
Number of participants is roughly constant from 2016 to 2017, gradually decreasing from 2017 to 2018, and lastly roughly constant from 2018 to 2019.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Number of participants, about 2299700.0 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Number of participants, of value 2056900.0 was reported at Year 2019
